{"books":[{"id":"92a9726b-e187-4276-b399-71f6383e4d2d","name":"红旗一九七一年第十二期","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"《红旗》杂志编辑部","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives2/main/92a9726b-e187-4276-b399-71f6383e4d2d.pdf"],"article":{"title":"三大纪律八项注意","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"三大纪律八项注意"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红军歌曲.1 = A 4/4"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"2·3"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"26"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"33.5.312"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"6"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"3"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"62.3"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"55"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"+"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"·"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"意："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三大纪律八项注1.革命军人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个要牢记，2.第二不拿群众一针线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群众对我拥护又喜欢；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八项注意切莫忘记了：3.三大纪律我们要做到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公买公卖不许遥霸道；4.第"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"买卖价钱要公平，二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照价赔偿不差半分毫；5.第"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四若把东西损坏了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行军作战处处注意到；6.第六爱护群众的庄稼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不许打骂不许搜腰包；7.第八不许虐待俘虏兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民战士处处爱人民，8.革命纪律条条要记清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"2-123 222532"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"62.1 2362"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"■"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"步调一致才能得胜利；1. 第-"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"切行动听指挥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"努力减轻人民的负担。2.第三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"切缴获要归公，1"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尊重群"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羊众不要要骄傲；3.第—"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说话态度要和好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还切莫遗失掉；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当面归4.第三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"借人东西用过了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军阀作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风坚决克服掉；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"许打人和骂人，5.第五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流氓习"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"气坚决要除掉；6.第七"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"许调戏妇女们，不"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"互相监督切莫违犯了。7.遵守纪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"律人人要自觉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全国人民拥护又欢迎。8.保卫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖，国永远向前进，"}],"authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1971,"month":11,"day":1}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":14,"page_end":14},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}